    <a id="main-content"></a>
            <div class="element-invisible">    <h1 class="title" id="page-title">Common Configurations</h1>
    </div>                    <section class="block block-menu-block block-13 block-menu-block-13 odd" id="block-menu-block-13">
  <div class="block-inner clearfix">
              <h2 class="block-title">Installing + Configuring</h2>
            
    <div class="content clearfix">
      <div class="menu-block-wrapper menu-block-13 menu-name-main-menu parent-mlid-2605 menu-level-1">
  <ul class="menu"><li class="first leaf menu-mlid-2606"><a href="/fr/docs/cck/installing-configuring/install-ubiquiti-router">Install on a Ubiquiti Router</a></li>
<li class="leaf menu-mlid-2750"><a href="/fr/docs/cck/installing-configuring/configure-commotion">Configure Commotion</a></li>
<li class="leaf active-trail active menu-mlid-2751"><a href="/fr/docs/cck/installing-configuring/common-configurations" title="This document describes several common configurations for Commotion nodes other than the default." class="active-trail active">Common Configurations</a></li>
<li class="leaf menu-mlid-2749"><a href="/fr/docs/cck/installing-configuring/troubleshoot-your-wireless-node">Troubleshoot Your Wireless Node</a></li>
<li class="last leaf menu-mlid-2607"><a href="/fr/node/9511">Install and Recover with TFTP</a></li>
</ul></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section><div class="block block-system block-main block-system-main even block-without-title" id="block-system-main">
